{
 "file": "_STGSP1A.bin",
 "source_size": 34832,
 "built_size": 37564,
 "edits": [
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x150e",
   "jp_len": 162,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "{00}ゃ{00}う{00}る{00}の{00}行{00}『{00}き{00}じ{00}！{00}M{00}思{00}{01}{01}て{00}{01}{01}サ{00}{01}{01}2{00}{01}{01}Sぁあいうえおかダチッツテ{01}デ、トドナ。ネハバパ·々ビベブミメちっつぞラてリずン下がー我とぬ開』官きの間ばは機貴カ近軍見まむ向行みすじせね国そやよ佐士死·{00}！ジ{00}Mせのな、{00}{01}！た{00}M捕ぬな、{00}{01}ぁ希望住在宇宙的所有人都能听我一言……",
   "zh_hex": ""
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15b0",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我名叫夏亚·阿兹纳布尔",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce8ace8c1ef37e7d6ef4be7d2e856e882e831e7e1000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15be",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我乃吉翁共和国创始者吉翁·兹姆·戴肯{00}之子！",
   "zh_hex": "158befdde7d9ee88ea48e7d3a1e893e908ade7d9ee8804e856e82304eb06e93d00e7cde88606000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15da",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "当年、家父吉翁向联邦要求确立宇宙居民{00}的自治权之时、",
   "zh_hex": "15c4e90902e7dfe888e7d9ee889def2ed1ef2ae93ae88ce86be8bee8bfea4cef3800e7b4abea79eb39e7cdef2d0200000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15fc",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "扎比家暗杀了家父、盗用公国之名、向地{00}球联邦发动了独立战争",
   "zh_hex": "15e84be825e7dfea6ae89be7bae7dfe88802e9f3d8e9a4a1e7cde8ac029dbf0095ef2ed1e870ef30e7bae8eee86bef28e852000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1623",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "其结果诸君也都清楚、最终以吉翁公国的{00}败北而告终",
   "zh_hex": "15e8cfe868e871ea5697e7c0e840e995ebd302e8c5e8e2e7f3e7d9ee88e9a4a1e7b400e88febb7e89ce8e5e8e2000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1643",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那倒也罢了！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e848e7c0eaefe7baef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x164e",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "然而、联邦政府却因此愈发骄横、竟炮制{00}出提坦斯那样的组织",
   "zh_hex": "15e7efe89c02ef2eefaaea68ea60eadfef33e7caed5fe870edcbec7702ef2ce95ae8de00efbee821e843e7c8e7b7e7dae7b4ea0deb3f000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1672",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "事到如今、我已深信、绝不能再让人类重{00}燃战火！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb8e7d7e7f0efb902efccef3aeb0de90f02e91ce7b5e7c6e80be7f9efb2e841e8a100eb93ef28e8daef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1696",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "而这一切的元凶……",
   "zh_hex": "15e89ce7b9efb6ef3fe7b4ecaeecb209090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16a1",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正是那些只顾自己、死赖在地球上不肯离{00}去的人们！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3be7b6e7b7e8a4ef32ea1fefb5e8c902ef6aeb46ef29ef63efd3ef4ce7b5e93de90100e7ebe7b4efb2e7bbef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16c2",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "故此、我夏亚·阿兹纳布尔、在此宣告新{00}吉翁成立、同时……",
   "zh_hex": "15ea09e7ca028bef37e7d604e7d2e856e882e831e7e102ef29e7caeccce8e5ef8a00e7d9ee88e837e86b02e85def2d0909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16e3",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正式向地球联邦政府宣战！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3bea26efc1ef63efd3ef2eefaaea68ea60ecccef28ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1710",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚……！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d60909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1733",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "还以为他失踪了、没想到竟在暗中筹划着{00}这种大事",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f7e7f3e7c1e80ce8a5ec97e7ba02e7d8e7e6e7d7ef2cef29ea6aef4eecf7ea74e86d00e7b9e7d1efa5efb8000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1770",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "上一场战争中曾并肩作战的那位……究竟{00}是为了什么呢？",
   "zh_hex": "15b287e876ef28e852c0ea2ae957eb16ef2fef28e7b4e7b7e8340909e906ef2c00e7b6e7c1e7bae7dde7bde9070500000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17b7",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是要做个了断……吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6ef2ae81ce828e7bae9820909e7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17dd",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……了断？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7bae982050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1800",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他和我们并肩战斗过、早就厌透了联邦政{00}府的那套做法",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce7d3efcce7bbe957eb16ef28e7ffef3602e963e7c5eb2bed10e7baef2eefaaea6800ea60e7b4e7b7eb30e81ce84e000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1821",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "于是、他下定决心要把这一切都做个了断{00}所以才……",
   "zh_hex": "15e879e7b602e80c89e867e8abe82def2ae81be7b987ef3fe840e81ce828e7bae98200e7fbe7f3e8360909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x188c",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "布莱特舰长！军总部发来紧急通讯！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e831e846e7cfe7d4ef3406e7e0e881cce870d9eaedea62c2eb1b06060000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x189f",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "新、新吉翁他们……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8a02ef8ae7d9ee88e80ce7bb0909060600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18c9",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么了！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bde7baef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18ec",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是殖民地坠落！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e8a9ef38ef63eb53e92aef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18f7",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "通讯说、新吉翁让第5月神{00}坠向了地球！！",
   "zh_hex": "15c2eb1be7ed02ef8ae7d9ee88e7f9e940ec03e850e9aa00eb539de7babf95060600000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1930",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你说什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7ede7dde7bdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1954",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚……！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d60909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1973",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "…………",
   "zh_hex": "150909090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19a1",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d6ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19c3",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是阿姆罗吗？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e7d2e823e7ece802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19e7",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚！你为什么、要把那种东西朝地球抛{00}下去！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d6ef97e7b8e7c1e7dde7bd02ef2ae81be7b7e7d1e8bae7f8eaadef63efd3eaa900ef4de7ebef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19fe",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这么一来、地球就会变冷、再也住不了人{00}了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7bdefb6efcf02ef63efd3e7c5e7e2e955eb4e02e80be7c0e859e7b5e7baefb200e7baef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a34",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "住在地球上的那些人、根本只顾着自己！",
   "zh_hex": "15e859ef29ef63efd3ef4ce7b4e7b7e8a4efb202e9b8efa6ef32ea1fe86defb5e8c9ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a50",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所以我才宣告、要将他们尽数抹杀！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe7f3efcce836eccce8e502ef2ae84ae80ce7bbe8f2e914ecd9e89bef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a84",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿姆罗、纵然是你、若敢阻挠我、我也绝{00}不留情！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e823e7ec02e8e6e7efe7b6e7b802e7e7e8cde8efed66efcc02efcce7c0e91c00e7b5e98ce88bef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ac5",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！人凭什么审判人……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909ef97efb2ea49e7dde7bdeccaeb29efb20909ef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b00",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "新吉翁军的MS、已经展开了！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8ae7d9ee88e7e0e7b4131402ef3ae8b7e989e7fae7ba0606000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b2b",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "迎击！全体人员、进入战斗态势！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e931e7ccef97efb4ef4fefb2e84902e892e891ef28e7ffe994e8fdef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b67",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶……不妙！我们正好撞进了激战的正{00}中央！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7de0909e7b5ecc7ef97efcce7bbef3be7c7ecdfe892e7bae9b9ef28e7b4ef3b00ef4eec5aef97ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ba1",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么了？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bde7ba050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bc3",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊、参谋次官……新吉翁和隆德·贝尔、{00}好像交上手了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c302ed1aea6ee8648f0909ef8ae7d9ee88e7d3ed16e82c04e857e7e10200e7c7e8e9e861b2aee7ba090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bff",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要能按时赶到伦德尼恩就行……这点风{00}险、我早有觉悟",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2ae7c6ea76ef2dea04e7d7ea5be82ce896e7eee7c5efd60909e7b9e822eb7500e93202efcce963e7cbe8aeea190000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c37",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么了、爸？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bde7ba02ec2a050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c5f",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "没什么事、你回座位上去吧、奎丝",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d8e7dde7bdefb802e7b8ef52ebc4e834ef4ce7ebe7d002eb82e8a300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c92",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "…………",
   "zh_hex": "150909090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cb6",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……总之、计划不变、就照原样继续前进{00}吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e881e7cd02ea55ea74e7b5e95502e7c5ea1ae8e4e7dae9d6e9adef51e89200e7d000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ced",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d19",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "人岂能惩罚人……！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb2eac3e7c6ecd5eda5efb20909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d47",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "地球已经到了再也支撑不下去的时候了！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef63efd3ef3ae8b7e7d7e7bae80be7c0e883ea29e7b5ef4de7ebe7b4ef2dea39e7baef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d59",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所以、才要由我夏亚·阿兹纳布尔来动手{00}肃清、阿姆罗！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe7f302e836ef2ae8a6efccef37e7d6ef4be7d2e856e882e831e7e1efcfef30ef6600eb9de99502e7d2e823e7ecef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d97",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是自私！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6aba80606000000000000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1dc9",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "竟然做出这种事……我真是看错您了、克{00}瓦特罗大尉！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ce7efe81cefbee7b9e7d1efb80909efcce820e7b6e7f6e885e835e7ba02e7d500e99fe7cfe7ecefa5efc6ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e01",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "再这样下去、被重力束缚住灵魂的人们、{00}终将令地球走向毁灭……",
   "zh_hex": "15e80be7b9e7daef4de7eb02e7f1e8a1efb0e895eb9be859eaebeb4ae7b4efb2e7bb0200e8e2e84ae94eef63efd3e890efc1e97ce8e109090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e25",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我已经不能再当克瓦特罗了！明白吧、卡{00}缪！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef3ae8b7e7b5e7c6e80bef53e7d5e99fe7cfe7ece7baef97ef39e809e7d002e80100e917ef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e62",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这种歪理……！我无法接受、克瓦特罗大{00}尉！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7d1ec24e8720909ef97efcce7dce84eefcee8c802e7d5e99fe7cfe7ecefa500efc6ef97ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ea1",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ecd",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我再也不会、把您称作克瓦特罗大尉{00}了",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcce80be7c0e7b5e7e202e81be835ea01ef2fe7d5e99fe7cfe7ecefa5efc600e7ba00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1eed",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您就是夏亚·阿兹纳布尔……是这个世上{00}不该存在的人！",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e7c5e7b6ef37e7d6ef4be7d2e856e882e831e7e10909e7b6e7b9e828e83cef4c00e7b5e898e993ef29e7b4efb2ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f33",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "（这就是年轻吗……）",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8ee7b9e7c5e7b6e909e990e8020909ef8f000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f66",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "克瓦特罗！你这家伙、什么都没搞明白！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d5e99fe7cfe7ecef97e7b8e7b9e7dfe7fd02e7dde7bde840e7d8ec1cef39e809ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f80",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为了守护地球、却要污染地球！你脑子有{00}毛病吧……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1e7bae8a8e8e0ef63efd302eadfef2aec26ebd0ef63efd3ef97e7b8eb67e886e7cb00eb60ed8be7d00909ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fba",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "地球上的人若肯多为地球着想、我也不至{00}于走到这一步！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef63efd3ef4ce7b4efb2e7e7e93de7e9e7c1ef63efd3e86de7e602efcce7c0e7b5e89700e879e890e7d7e7b9efb6ea93ef97000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fde",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "要想救地球、如今只能由某个人来背负起{00}人类的罪业了、捷多！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ae7e6e8caef63efd302e7f0efb9ef32e7c6e8a6eae8e828efb2efcfe9e4e92ce84700efb2e841e7b4ea7feadae7ba02e7bce7e9ef97ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x202a",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是你吗、阿尔黛西亚……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e7b8e80202e7d2e7e1ea9ae7f8e7d60909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x204e",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "果然、还是变成了这副模样呢……卡斯巴{00}尔哥哥",
   "zh_hex": "15e871e7ef02e7f7e7b6e955e837e7bae7b9ecb6ea91e7dae9070909e801e7c8e85b00e7e1e9bce9bc000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2067",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "野心与妄想……到头来、你终究还是摆脱{00}不了它们",
   "zh_hex": "15eb21e82de832ecc6e7e60909e7d7e92eefcf02e7b8e8e2e906e7f7e7b6eb8be9e500e7b5e7bae978e7bb000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20a3",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不对、阿尔黛西亚……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7be02e7d2e7e1ea9ae7f8e7d60909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20b0",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我只不过、是想去做那些对人类而言必要{00}之事罢了！",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef32e7b5ef3602e7b6e7e6e7ebe81ce7b7e8a4e7beefb2e841e89cefd7e860ef2a00e7cdefb8eaefe7baef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20f8",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "住手吧、夏亚！",
   "zh_hex": "15e859ef66e7d002ef37e7d6ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2109",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你难道不明白、自己正在重蹈我曾犯下的{00}过错吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e866e82ae7b5ef39e80902abe8c9ef3bef29e8a1eeae8bea2aeb0e89e7b400ef36e885e802060500000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2149",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你曾说过、在人类觉醒为新人类之前、地{00}球就会先一步走向毁灭",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8ea2ae7edef3602ef29efb2e841e8aeeb20e7c1ef8aefb2e841e7cdef5102ef6300efd3e7c5e7e2ef8befb6ea93e890efc1e97ce8e1000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x216f",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "经历过这些战斗、我已明白、你当年那番{00}话是对的",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b7e8fbef36e7b9e8a4ef28e7ff02efccef3aef39e80902e7b8ef53e909e7b7ee6d00e81fe7b6e7bee7b4000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21aa",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不对！那是个错误啊、夏亚！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7beef97e7b7e7b6e828e885ea33e7c302ef37e7d6ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21db",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你若是要阻挠我、哈曼……纵然是你、我{00}也绝不留情！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7e7e7b6ef2ae8efed66efcc02e7e8e8740909e8e6e7efe7b6e7b802efcc00e7c0e91ce7b5e98ce88bef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2218",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d60909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2246",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你之前曾对我说过、要和我重新来过……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7cdef51ea2ae7beefcce7edef3602ef2ae7d3efcce8a1ef8aefcfef36090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2262",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那番话、难道是骗我的吗、夏亚！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7ee6de81f02e866e82ae7b6eb498be7b4e80202ef37e7d606050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2295",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对你、我深感抱歉、哈曼……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7bee7b802efcceb0de87de922e92702e7e8e8740909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22ac",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可是、要改变如今这个世界、我除此之外{00}别无他法！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b602ef2ae9f0e955e7f0efb9e7b9e828e83ce8f502efcce974e7cae7cde8f700e7e5e7dce80ce84eef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22f4",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "真没想到、你竟是会干出这等惊天大事的{00}人……",
   "zh_hex": "15e820e7d8e7e6e7d702e7b8ef2ce7b6e7e2e8d3efbee7b9e826ec6de844efa5efb8e7b400efb20909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2312",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你就没有重新考虑的打算吗、克瓦特罗大{00}尉？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7c5e7d8e7cbe8a1ef8aeb41eba1e7b4e7f5e889e80202e7d5e99fe7cfe7ecefa500efc605000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2341",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那个名字早已成为过去了",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e828e8ace980e963ef3ae837e7c1ef36e7ebe7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x236e",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来你是打定主意、要以夏亚的身份行动{00}到底了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6efcfe7b8e7b6e7f5e867e954ef3c02ef2ae7f3ef37e7d6e7b4e88dea22efd6ef3000e7d7e9b4e7ba090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2383",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、你就是我们的敌人了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e7b8e7c5e7b6efcce7bbe7b4e7e3efb2e7baef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23b9",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为了改变世界、就非得让这么多人去死不{00}可吗……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1e7bae9f0e955e83ce8f502e7c5e8f0e80ae7f9e7b9e7bde7e9efb2e7ebef6ae7b500e7c4e8020909ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23d9",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这根本不对劲啊、克瓦特罗大尉！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9b8efa6e7b5e7beeb50e7c302e7d5e99fe7cfe7ecefa5efc6ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2404",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那只不过是一个驾驶员的想法罢了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7ef32e7b5ef36e7b687e828e953e975e849e7b4e7e6e84eeaefe7ba06000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2418",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "如今地球已经撑不下去了、我已经顾不上{00}挑选手段了！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f0efb9ef63efd3ef3ae8b7ea29e7b5ef4de7ebe7ba02efccef3ae8b7ea1fe7b5ef4c00eae7e966ef66ea6be7baef97ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x245f",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "战争好不容易才结束、{00}迎来了和平……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef28e852e7c7e7b5ed2fe964e836e868e8950200e931d9e7bae7d3e8870909060600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2478",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为什么、又非得挑起战争不可呢！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1e7dde7bd02e8f1e8f0e80aeae7e847ef28e852e7b5e7c4e907ef97050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24b3",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这世上、也有些东西、是茫然度日所无法{00}得到的……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e83cef4c02e7c0e7cbe8a4e8bae7f802e7b6ec37e7efe96de98ae7fbe7dce84e00e80ae7d7e7b40909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24d7",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你要明白这一点、基拉·大和！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8ef2aef39e809e7b9efb6e82202e829e7c2ef4befa5e7d3ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x250e",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你心里也一定、对如今联邦的所作所为存{00}有疑问吧……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e82def31e7c0efb6e86702e7bee7f0efb9ef2eefaae7b4e7fbef2fe7fbe7c1e99300e7cbeb62e997e7d00909ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x252d",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可你为何、还要任由联邦那群蠢货、利用{00}你的那份力量！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b8e7c18a02e7f7ef2ae89ae8a6ef2ed1e7b7ecfae94beaf502e82ed800e7b8e7b4e7b7ea22dae85106050000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x256d",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您太心急了……夏亚·阿兹纳布尔！",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e86ae82dea62e7ba0909ef37e7d6ef4be7d2e856e882e831e7e1ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2583",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正如您曾说过的那样、静待人们靠自己去{00}改变、不就好了吗！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3be7f0e835ea2ae7edef36e7b4e7b7e7da02eab3eaa8efb2e7bbe8c7efb5e8c9e7eb00e9f0e95502e7b5e7c5e7c7e7bae802ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25a9",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "如今的您、正打算重蹈我父亲曾犯下的过{00}错！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f0efb9e7b4e83502ef3be7f5e889e8a1eeaeefcce888e894ea2aeb0eef4de7b4ef3600e885ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25ee",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你就是阿姆罗·雷吧！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7c5e7b6e7d2e823e7ec04e8afe7d0060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25fd",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要打倒你、我就能证明、我比大佐还要{00}强！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2ae7f5e848e7b8028be7c5e7c6eba3ef39028be825bea3e7f7ef2a00e8ad060000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2637",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "搞什么、这家伙……？",
   "zh_hex": "15ec1ce7dde7bd02e7b9e7dfe7fd0909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2668",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……到此为止了",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7d7e7cae7c1e869e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2673",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "最初的目的已经达成了！全机、撤退！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8c5eb4fe7b4efd4e7b4ef3ae8b7ef2be837e7baef97efb4e7e402e90ae880ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26b3",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d6ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26d5",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要地球联邦还是现在这副模样、我就绝{00}不会停止战斗",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2abf95ef2ed1e7f7e7b6e82fef29e7b9ecb6ea91e7da028be7c5e91c00e7b5e7e2e934e869ef28e7ff00000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26f5",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……下次相见之时、便是我与你做个了断{00}之日、阿姆罗！",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef4de864e8b1e85ce7cdef2d02e8fae7b6efcce832e7b8e81ce828e7bae98200e7cde98a02e7d2e823e7ecef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2737",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2763",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是阿迪纳瓦参谋次官吗？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e7d2ea11e882e99fed1aea6ee8648fe802050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x278c",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "据说他就在我们刚才护卫的那艘穿梭机上",
   "zh_hex": "15e8cce7ede80ce7c5ef29efcce7bbe8bce836e8e0e9b2e7b4e7b7eb18ea7eeb8fe7e4ef4c00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27a6",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他身负政府的特别命令、希望由我们护送{00}他前往殖民地……",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce88de92cea68ea60e7b4e7cfe7e5e853e94e02e87be965e8a6efcce7bbe8e0e9ba00e80cef51e911e8a9ef38ef6309090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27e4",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……好、就见见吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c702e7c5e85ce85ce7d0000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x280c",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……唔！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e81def970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2813",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您是说、要和夏亚进行交涉……当真要这{00}么做吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e7b6e7ed02ef2ae7d3ef37e7d6e892efd6e861ece60909ef53e820ef2ae7b900e7bde81ce802ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2847",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "新吉翁通过非正式渠道、提出了会谈的请{00}求",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8ae7d9ee88c2ef36e8f0ef3bea26ee56e82a02e821afe7bae7e2eaf4e7b4e83a00e93a0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2865",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他们说、只要承认其独立、夏亚就会解散{00}军队",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce7bbe7ed02ef32ef2aea75e8a0e8cfe8eee86b02ef37e7d6e7c5e7e2e89def6800e7e0e7c9000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2883",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为了筹备接收事宜、我必须赶往月神2",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1e7baecf7e877b7e926a9ecc9028be860e9a2ea04e911e850e9aa0f00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28b9",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可是、第5月神那件事……夏亚不是已经{00}出动军队了吗！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b602e940ec03e850e9aae7b7e991a90909ef37e7d6e7b5e7b6ef3ae8b700afef30e7e0e7c9e7bae80206000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28f6",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那不过是示威罢了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b5ef36e7b6eab0e96beaefe7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x290a",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚其实、内心里是惧怕与联邦军正面冲{00}突的",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d6e8cfe87f02e99ae82def31e7b6ec6ee958e832ef2eefaae7e0ef3be862e95e00e8b6e7b4000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2940",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您根本就不了解夏亚的本性啊！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e9b8efa6e7c5e7b5e7bae89def37e7d6e7b4efa6e951e7c3ef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2974",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "总之、这是既定的决策、轮不到前线指挥{00}官来插嘴",
   "zh_hex": "15e881e7cd02e7b9e7b6e8c4e867e7b4e8abebe402ebf4e7b5e7d7ef51e916e8c0e94900ef92efcfeb08eae2000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29d6",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……明白了",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef39e809e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29e1",
   "jp_len": 41,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、将参谋次官护送到月神2之后、请{00}允许我们采取独立行动",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e84aed1aea6ee8648fe8e0e9bae7d7e850e9aa0fe7cde7fe02e83a00ecade8a78be7bbec9ee987e8eee86b9fef30000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a0a",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这样可以吧、参谋次官？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7dae7c4e7f3e7d002ed1aea6ee8648f0500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a36",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是自然、只要你们判断地球身陷危机、{00}随时都可以行动",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6efb5e7ef02ef32ef2ae7b8e7bbeb29e982ef63efd3e88deaf9e935e7e40200e9a1ef2de840e7c4e7f3efd6ef30000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a53",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "隆德·贝尔队、不正是为此而存在的吗",
   "zh_hex": "15ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c902e7b5ef3be7b6e7c1e7cae89ce993ef29e7b4e802000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a7d",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a9b",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……情况怎么样？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e88be8d0e7f2e7bde7da05000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ac5",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "目前看来、精神感应框架还没有出现什么{00}变化呢",
   "zh_hex": "15d5bae7f6d902e98de9aae87de873eef3e99de7f7e7d8e7cbafe82fe7dde7bd00e955e9a5e907000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ae1",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "备用零件我倒是备好了、不过照这情形看{00}来……",
   "zh_hex": "15e877efb3eb74e991efcce848e7b6e877e7c7e7ba02e7b5ef36ea1ae7b9e88bec67e7f600efcf090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b24",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……啊、阿姆罗·雷……",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c302e7d2e823e7ec04e8af090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b32",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "喂！你、就是那个阿姆罗·雷吧！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bd06e7b802e7c5e7b6e7b7e828e7d2e823e7ec04e8afe7d0060500000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b83",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你……是刚才那艘穿梭机上的那个孩子吧{00}？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b80909e7b6e8bce836e7b7eb18ea7eeb8fe7e4ef4ce7b4e7b7e828e956e886e7d000050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2bb8",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我叫奎丝·帕拉雅",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce8c1eb82e8a3ef4beb01e7c2ebfd000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2bde",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不好意思、奎丝·帕拉雅……这里是平民{00}不能擅自进入的地方",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7c7ef3cefca02eb82e8a3ef4beb01e7c2ebfd0909e7b9ef31e7b6e887ef3800e7b5e7c6eb5defb5e892e891e7b4ef63efb1000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c02",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我让人领你回去、你还是先回穿梭机上吧{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7f9efb2ea20e7b8ef52e7eb02e7b8e7f7e7b6ef8bef52ea7eeb8fe7e4ef4ce7d0000909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c44",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "喂、你是谁啊？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bd02e7b8e7b6e923e7c305000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c6a",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……诶？",
   "zh_hex": "150909eaf3050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c8c",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你怎么会在这里！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7f2e7bde7e2ef29e7b9ef31ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2cb6",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！？要问为什么……因为我是机械师啊{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def9705ef2ae997e7c1e7dde7bd0909ef33e7c1efcce7b6e7e4eb90e96ce7c300090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ce9",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "才不是！",
   "zh_hex": "15e836e7b5e7b6ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2cf4",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是问、凭什么是你待在阿姆罗的身边啊{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6e99702ea49e7dde7bde7b6e7b8eaa8ef29e7d2e823e7ece7b4e88de899e7c300ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d27",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b80909ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d4b",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿姆罗可是联邦最顶尖的新人类、不是吗{00}！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e823e7ece7c4e7b6ef2eefaae8c5eca1ee10e7b4ef8aefb2e84102e7b5e7b6e80200ef9705000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d63",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你是懂得这件事的分量、才待在那儿的吗{00}！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b6e8b0e80ae7b9e991a9e7b4cde85102e836eaa8ef29e7b7eb7ce7b4e802000605000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d98",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "喂、你……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bd02e7b809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2dbc",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不是『你』！我叫奎丝！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7b60ce7b80def97efcce8c1eb82e8a3ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2de7",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "奎丝……",
   "zh_hex": "15eb82e8a309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e09",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我只不过、是对身为新人类的阿姆罗·雷{00}感兴趣罢了！",
   "zh_hex": "158bef32e7b5ef3602e7b6e7bee88de7c1ef8ab4e841e7b4e7d2e823e7ec04e8af00e87deabaea82eaefe7ba060000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e27",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我只是想见见他、聊上几句！可这女人偏{00}要来碍事……！",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef32e7b6e7e6e85ce85ce80c02ec36ef4ceaa5ebb9ef97e7c4e7b9efadefb2eb4d00ef2aefcfe8c6efb80909ef97000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e4d",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿姆罗才不该把这种女人留在身边呢！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e823e7ece836e7b5e898e81be7b9e7d1efadefb2e98cef29e88de899e907ef97ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e84",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "别闹了、奎丝！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e5ead8e7ba02eb82e8a3ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e90",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对第一次见面的人、摆出这种态度也太失{00}礼了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7bee940efb6e864e85ce862e7b4efb202eb8befbee7b9e7d1e994e96de7c0e86ae8a500eb65e7ba00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ec7",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就是因为这样、大人们才……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7b6ef33e7c1e7b9e7da02efa5efb2e7bbe8360909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ed5",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "够了……阿姆罗就和那女人好好过日子去{00}吧！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e920e7ba0909e7d2e823e7ece7c5e7d3e7b7efadefb2e7c7e7c7ef36e98ae886e7eb00e7d0ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f40",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那孩子、到底是怎么回事……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e956e88602e7d7e9b4e7b6e7f2e7bdef52efb80909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f6a",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "听说她是阿迪纳瓦参谋次官的女儿……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d1e7ede88ee7b6e7d2ea11e882e99fed1aea6ee8648fe7b4b0eb7c0909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f83",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "…………",
   "zh_hex": "150909090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f8c",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "（那种感应方式……真危险啊）",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8ee7b7e7d1e87de873efb1ea260909e820e935e932e7c3ef8f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2fb3",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "真没想到会落到这般田地、大佐……我可{00}要怨您了",
   "zh_hex": "15e820e7d8e7e6e7d7e7e2e92ae7d7e7b9ea80efa0bf02bea309098be7c400ef2aec19e835e7ba0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ff0",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对不住了、罗伯托",
   "zh_hex": "15e7bee7b5e859e7ba02e7eceaa4e7f40000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ffb",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可我、有着即便与你们为敌、也非做不可{00}之事！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4efcc02e7cbe86de855e8fae832e7b8e7bbe7c1e7e302e7c0e8f0e81ce7b5e7c400e7cdefb8ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3043",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "大佐！这、到底是怎么回事啊！？",
   "zh_hex": "15efa5efbaef97e7b902e7d7e9b4e7b6e7f2e7bdef52efb8e7c3ef97050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3058",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "大佐您、竟然成了我们的敌人……",
   "zh_hex": "15efa5efbae83502ef2ce7efe837e7baefcce7bbe7b4e7e3efb2090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3090",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我再也不能、放任地上的人类继续污染地{00}球了！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce80be7c0e7b5e7c602e86ce89aef63ef4ce7b4efb2e841e9d6e9adec26ebd0ef6300efd3e7baef970000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x30b2",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对不住了、阿波利！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7bee7b5e859e7ba02e7d2e9a8e82e06000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7aae",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不好！这艘舰要是被击沉、那可就{00}……！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b5e7c706e7b9eb18e7d4ef2ae7b6e7f1e7cce98302e7b7e7c4e7c500090906000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7b46",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这一路征战、辛苦你了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9efb6e8d2ecd2ef2802ea58e9e6e7b8e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7b53",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "感谢你将这条『宇宙世纪路线』一路游玩{00}到了最后",
   "zh_hex": "15e87de8b2e7b8e84ae7b9e9d40ce8bee8bfe83ceb99e8d2e9160defb6e8d2ea94e97000e7d7e7bae8c5e7fe000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7b73",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另外、隆德·贝尔队的征战、就先在此告{00}一段落了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e99be8f702ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e7b4ecd2ef2802e7c5ef8bef29e7cae8e500efb6ea6be92ae7ba0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7b92",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过游戏本身仍可继续下去、今后也请你{00}继续尽情游玩",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef36ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9adef4de7eb02efb9e7fee7c0e83ae7b800e9d6e9ade8f2e88bea94e97000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7bb7",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另外、为一路通关本路线的你、还特意准{00}备了一个特别关卡",
   "zh_hex": "15e99be8f702e7c1efb6e8d2ef59e8bbefa6e8d2e916e7b4e7b802e7f7e7cfef3ce87a00e877e7baefb6e828e7cfe7e5e8bbe8010000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7bde",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是与我们分头作战至今的大天使队之间{00}的特别演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e832efcce7bbefaee92eef2fef28e897efb9e7b4efa5e844e83fe7c9e7cde8fc00e7b4e7cfe7e5ea2feab600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7bff",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "和他们交手一番、亲自检验你培养至今的{00}部队实力、也是件好事",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d3e80ce7bbe861ef66efb6ee6d02e894efb5ee40ea99e7b8edfeec0be897efb9e7b400ef70e7c9e87fefb002e7c0e7b6e991e7c7efb80000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7c24",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特别演习』、便能与{00}他们一决高下",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29abe8a6e7beef28c0e966eaaa0ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d02e8fae7c6e83200e80ce7bb87e8abe812890000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7c49",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、就请继续游玩『SD高达G世{00}代DS』吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd02e7c5e83ae9d6e9adea94e9700cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83c00e8e7ef96ef9e0de7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7c6d",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后也希望你能静下心来、尽情玩到最后",
   "zh_hex": "15efb9e7fee7c0e87be965e7b8e7c6eab3ef4de82defcf02e8f2e88be970e7d7e8c5e7fe00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7ce6",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "谢谢你一路以来、一直陪着我这个不太靠{00}得住的舰长",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b2e8b2e7b8efb6e8d2e7f3efcf02efb6e875ef42e86defcce7b9e828e7b5e86ae8c700e80ae859e7b4e7d4ef3400000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d05",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『平成高达路线』、就到此告一段落{00}了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce887e837e812ef2be8d2e9160d02e7c5e7d7e7cae8e5efb6ea6be92a00e7ba000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d23",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽说、我们预防者的这场战斗、是已经结{00}束了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7ed02efcce7bbea5ae968ef6ee7b4e7b9e876ef28e7ff02e7b6ef3ae8b7e86800e895e7ba090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d3d",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不过游戏本身也还能继续下去哦、今{00}后也请你继续享受游戏吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b5ef36ea94ea3eefa6e88de7c0e7f7e7c6e9d6e9adef4de7ebe91902efb900e7fee7c0e83ae7b8e9d6e9adec06e8c8ea94ea3ee7d00000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d63",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为一路玩通这条路线的你、还另外准备了{00}全新的关卡哦",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1efb6e8d2e970ef59e7b9e9d4e8d2e916e7b4e7b802e7f7e99be8f7e87ae877e7ba00efb4ef8ae7b4e8bbe801e9190000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d87",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是与我们分头、和提坦斯及新吉翁交过{00}手的……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e8328be7bbcde92e02e7d3e821e843e7c8e9cfef8ae7d9ee88e861ef3600aee7b40909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7da2",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……正是和那支隆德·贝尔队之间的特别{00}演习哦",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef3be7b6e7d3e7b7e883ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e7cde8fce7b4e7cfe7e500ea2feab6e9190000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7db5",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特别演习』、就能和{00}他们一战了哦",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efb5e8a6e7beef28ef4ee966eaaa0ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d02e7c5e7c6e7d300e80ce7bbefb6ef28e7bae9190000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7ddb",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请你一定要去挑战看看哦",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae7b8efb6e867ef2ae7ebeae7ef28e7f6e7f6e9190000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7de9",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、就请继续游玩『SD高达G世{00}代DS』吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd02e7c5e83ae9d6e9adea94e9700cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83c00e8e7ef96ef9e0de7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7e0d",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『自由对战的战火！尽情冲杀吧、大天使{00}号！！』",
   "zh_hex": "150cefb5e8a6e7beef28e7b4ef28e8daef97e8f2e88be95ee89be7d002efa5e844e83f00e833ef97ef970d000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7e8e",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是主天使号的舰长、娜塔尔·巴基露露{00}中佐",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6e954e844e83fe833e7b4e7d4ef3402e7eae945e7e1ef4be85be829e858e85800ef4eefba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7e9e",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "首先、请允许我向你一路以来出色的指挥{00}、致以由衷的敬意",
   "zh_hex": "15ef40b802e83aecade8a78b9de7b887e8d2e7f3d9afe89fe7b4e8c0e9490002ea32e7f3e8a6edb3e7b4ee38ef3c000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7ec0",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正是多亏了你的协助、我们才终于得以奋{00}战到最后",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3be7b6e7e9eab7e7bae7b8e7b4e8f6ea2302efcce7bbe836e8e2e879e80ae7f3ef4600ef28e7d7e8c5e7fe000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7ee2",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『对手路线』、就到此结束了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce7beef66e8d2e9160d02e7c5e7d7e7cae868e895e7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7ef8",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽说、我们主天使队的这场战斗、是已经{00}到此结束了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7ed02efcce7bbe954e844e83fe7c9e7b4e7b9e876ef28e7ff02e7b6ef3ae8b700e7d7e7cae868e895e7ba090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7f11",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过游戏本身仍可继续下去、今后也请你{00}继续尽情游玩",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef36ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9adef4de7eb02efb9e7fee7c0e83ae7b800e9d6e9ade8f2e88bea94e970000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7f35",
   "jp_len": 43,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "自由对战今后仍可继续下去、另外、只要{00}选择『特别演习』……",
   "zh_hex": "15efb5e8a6e7beef28efb9e7feeab9e7c4e9d6e9adef4de7eb02e99be8f702ef32ef2a00e966eaaa0ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d0909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7f60",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "便能与隆德·贝尔、预防者一同进行一场{00}联合演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e8fae7c6e832ed16e82cef4be857e7e102ea5ae968ef6eefb6e85de892efd6efb6e87600ef2eefc0ea2feab6000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7f7e",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我坚信、以你的本领、在与他们的战斗中{00}也定能克敌制胜",
   "zh_hex": "15efcceb80e90f02e7f3e7b8e7b4efa6ea2002ef29e832e80ce7bbe7b4ef28e7ffef4e00e7c0e867e7c6e7d5e7e3e8dee8db00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7fa3",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、就请继续游玩『SD高达G世{00}代DS』吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd02e7c5e83ae9d6e9adea94e9700cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83c00e8e7ef96ef9e0de7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7fc7",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后也愿你武运长久、奋战不息",
   "zh_hex": "15efb9e7fee7c0e961e7b8e8ece986ef34e9db02ef46ef28e7b5ec6a000000"
  }
 ]
}
